{"tid":1803551,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"曱甴：歡迎民陣與暴力割席","createTime":"2019-12-30T09:28:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T11:48:39.000Z","uid":216992,"like":23,"dislike":63,"uniUserReply":72,"replies":[{"pid":"dd7bd0c8d5e914b868adbddfb8515315af450d88","tid":1803551,"uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T09:28:55.000Z","msg":"民陣元旦日發起遊行，獲警方發出不反對通知書。民陣表示，網上「毋忘報仇 全民裝修」的遊行海報改圖，並非屬於民陣。警察公共關係科總警司郭嘉銓說，歡迎民陣與暴力割席，又呼籲當日大會不要為暴力行為掩飾，市民要提高警覺、和平地集會，如當日有突發事件，要聽從警方指示。<br />\n<br />\n港島總區警司曾繁瀚表示，警方一如既往，會在遊行集會一帶地方做人流管制，呼籲市民行用公共交通工具前往維園。遊行當日，警方會封閉全部西行線及部分電車路給遊行人士。曾繁瀚表示，當集會遊行不安全，警方可能會解散活動，呼籲市民及民陣配合，和平有序地參與集會遊行。他重申，警方不會容忍任何暴力事件。<br />\n<br />\n至於明晚除夕夜的安排，港島總區交通部執行及管制組總督察蕭奕騏表示，警方在銅鑼灣、灣仔、蘭桂坊、中區多個地方，按需要由下午2時起封路。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1500174-20191230.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1500174-20191230.htm&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkYgmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=4af393da\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1500174-20191230.htm&h=859c6e25\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1500174-20191230.htm</a>"},{"pid":"b15ddfed1ffa2426696276b9483894010232c667","tid":1803551,"uid":216992,"like":173,"dislike":1,"score":172,"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T09:29:51.000Z","msg":"市民要求警方澄清此圖。。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8nxvFxN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8nxvFxN.png&h=94a099e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好撚驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc7cf686b8fd7ef6585f4768a7e38437d925fd10","tid":1803551,"uid":317233,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"b15ddfed1ffa2426696276b9483894010232c667","tid":1803551,"uid":2169