 /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好驚呀點算"},{"pid":"9d15a6308351669d6d2b0cd4c2e4beaec4ddd9dc","tid":1803551,"uid":23085,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T09:44:39.000Z","msg":"民陣就假海報作出聲明。<br />\n<br />\n民陣昨日收到警方傳來一張假海報，並聲稱有人篡改民陣就元旦遊行的海報設計，改為呼籲抗爭者於 1 月 1 日進行「全城裝修」。<br />\n<br />\n民陣在警隊轉發海報予我方前，民陣從未於各 Telegram 公海、討論區發現相關改圖。根據傳媒報導，相關海報是在建制派支援者的社群網絡中開始流傳。民陣質疑警隊發出的假海報的來源。<br />\n<br />\n今日警方向民陣副召集人陳皓桓發出警告，指民陣如不作出澄清，或將涉嫌煽動。民陣在此清晰表示，被刪改海報上的內容違背了我們發起遊行的原意，作為「受害」一方，民陣竟再被警方威脅，實在是非常離譜，警隊應主動調查假海報來源，例如從上載假海報的建制派人士開始查起，而非要求我們作出澄清。<br />\n<br />\n警隊在今日的四時記者會上更稱「歡迎民陣與暴力割席」，民陣對相關言論百思不得其解，唯有在此重申，我們一定會與警察的暴力割席，自六月十二日中信鎮壓事件及其後至今的所有警暴，民陣都強烈、清晰地反對，而今日民陣在記者會就假海報的說明，是對 A 貨割席，不要搞錯。<br />\n<br />\n民間人權陣線<br />\n2019 年 12 月 30 日<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67122bca52510c8970c30c7f9e693e9b5b455764","tid":1803551,"uid":50553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b15ddfed1ffa2426696276b9483894010232c667","tid":1803551,"uid":216992,"like":173,"dislike":1,"score":172,"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T09:29:51.000Z","msg":"市民要求警方澄清此圖。。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8nxvFxN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8nxvFxN.png&h=94a099e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好撚驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T09:44:53.000Z","msg":"哇屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好撚驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91c564cf5c7ad897a0722a63b173e2acfb788bc1","tid":1803551,"uid":259493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T09:45:13.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n中共遲早要讓步、我們必須堅持下去<br />\n中共經濟只是紙老虎 ；在貿易協議， 大敗而回 。中國問題三座大山；<br />\n一、樓市泡沫 債務堆積如山 連恆大都要借十幾厘利息渡日<br />\n二、 貿易戰下 廠商大量出走 造成失業潮<br />\n三、壓力下，竟然推出[國進民退]， 集中阿里巴巴騰訊聯想等科技龍頭&hellip;的力量  專心工打5G/ 人工智能/大數據/超級電腦等領域，最終'大躍進'的2.0=必自毀前程<br />\n<br />\n香港勝在有大型反抗/黃色經濟圈、好讓美國視為新西柏林，不至於受到西方重點攻擊<br />\n藍絲不明白中共已敗象紛呈，現在美國吹雞，香港人就必須選邊站，明確支持美英歐日，方可逃出生天</span></strong>"},{"pid":"65b3793d39d2aa245b63d8b46e9f4f9fd1a83bf9","tid":1803551,"uid":147376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T09:45:46.000Z","msg":"狗狗嘅邏輯你係諗唔到 佢以為咁樣會分化到香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad21e211d60cfa1f0ade60a725246e799a026e37","tid":1803551,"uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42b334365356b5cb69c64f09f1d53a8a1c071b66","tid":1803551,"uid":329698,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fa9c0ec320505c3d6367934dd007170612245daf","tid":1803551,"uid":216992,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"526b396d45f4fce547099114ea19c08e1b8ed6a7","tid":1803551,"uid":34869,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T09:36:28.000Z","msg":"做場大龍鳳都係為左呢句姐<br />\n<br />\n但好撚肉酸囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T09:37:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />痴撚線 咩心態"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T09:41:33.000Z","msg":"