ote":{"pid":"bcdf51238b51829f89b9ffeabe9139f37c75c911","tid":1803551,"uid":169079,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T09:36:06.000Z","msg":"On9民陣有撚割裝修咩，佢割張假圖咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n放字入人地口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無恥到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T10:03:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><em><strong>其實佢哋越低莊我哋只會越團結</strong></em></span>"},{"pid":"1a595b11a7f8fd095ff54be445a6cda85a3fba11","tid":1803551,"uid":10152,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T10:04:16.000Z","msg":"民陣就假海報作出聲明。<br />\n<br />\n民陣昨日收到警方傳來一張假海報，並聲稱有人篡改民陣就元旦遊行的海報設計，改為呼籲抗爭者於 1 月 1 日進行「全城裝修」。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">民陣在警隊轉發海報予我方前，民陣從未於各 Telegram 公海、討論區發現相關改圖。</span>根據傳媒報導，相關海報是在建制派支援者的社群網絡中開始流傳。民陣質疑警隊發出的假海報的來源。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">今日警方向民陣副召集人陳皓桓發出警告，指民陣如不作出澄清，或將涉嫌煽動。民陣在此清晰表示，被刪改海報上的內容違背了我們發起遊行的原意，作為「受害」一方，民陣竟再被警方威脅，實在是非常離譜</span>，警隊應主動調查假海報來源，例如從上載假海報的建制派人士開始查起，而非要求我們作出澄清。<br />\n<br />\n警隊在今日的四時記者會上更稱「歡迎民陣與暴力割席」，民陣對相關言論百思不得其解，唯有在此重申，<span style=\"color: red;\">我們一定會與警察的暴力割席</span>，自六月十二日中信鎮壓事件及其後至今的所有警暴，民陣都強烈、清晰地反對，而今日民陣在記者會就假海報的說明，是對 A 貨割席，不要搞錯。<br />\n<br />\n民間人權陣線<br />\n2019 年 12 月 30 日<br />\n<br />\n#又唔讀書又唔做野<br />\n#得閒食海底撈Claim公數不如Claim公數進修下<br />\n#基本閱讀理解及聆聽<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n【民陣元旦大遊行】<br />\n2020.1.1 星期三 Wednesday｜2PM<br />\n維園中央草坪 遊行至 遮打道行人專用區<br />\nFrom Victoria Park (Central Lawn) to <br />\nChater Road Pedestrian Precinct<br />\n<br />\n*已取得不反對通知書<br />\n*Letter of No Objection Received<br />\n<br />\n【海報、單張下載】 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2QwFg31\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2QwFg31&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkYgmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=2d896400\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2QwFg31</a><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n【民陣 TG】 <a href=\"http://t.me/CivilHumanRightsFront\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FCivilHumanRightsFront&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkYgmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=3bfe62c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/CivilHumanRightsFront</a><br />\n【民陣 Twitter】 <a href=\"http://twitter.com/chrf_hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fchrf_hk&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkYgmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=6b4b8a24\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">twitter.com/chrf_hk</a><br />\n<br />\n民陣被捕法律支援熱線：6549 9452<br />\nWhatsapp / SMS / Telegram<br />\n<br />\n請提供資料：（＊必要）<br />\n <br />\n1. 被捕地點<br />\n2. 中文全名＊<br />\n3. 英文全名<br />\n4. 身份證號碼<br />\n5. 性別、年齡<br />\n6. 當事人電話<br />\n7. 所在警署<br />\n8. 緊急聯絡人電話＊<br />\n9. 報料人電話＊（若與緊急聯絡人不同）<br />\n10. 其他詳情（如有）"},{"pid":"53855e5701a23b20e3e20b26d6907d9e99d64885","tid":1803551,"uid":38991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T10:04:46.000Z","msg":"一個pprb總警司分化技巧仲衰過連登5毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲想加人工"},{"pid":"ef82c7aec3eed64ae1d8bcb580868d7595c186b1","tid":1803551,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53855e5701a23b20e3e20b26d6907d9e99d64885","tid":1803551,"uid":38991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T10:04:46.000Z","msg":"一個pprb總警司分化技巧仲衰過連登5毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲想加人工"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T10:05:47.000Z","msg":"近月先上連登學<br />\n係渣啲"},{"pid":"e51ad387a2e975660e31bc712425dc1ed3494426","tid":1803551,"uid":299436,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fe5e290b2db4910389033522e076cf4774d87f18","tid":1803551,"uid":5191,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T09:35:08.000Z","msg":"澄清唔係佢就係割席？乜撚野邏輯"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T10:06:46.000Z","msg":"依家連割唔割席都有得屈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" c